The,Recruitee,Public,API,provides,a,way,to,show,company,s,jobs,and,add,new,candidates,to,jobs,It,allows,you,to,access,answers,for,the,job,s,questions,and,includes,name,email,phone,and,more,The,API,does,not,require,authorization,all,you,need,is,your,company,s,subdomain,Recruitee,are,a,team,of,tech,loving,entrepreneurs,that,provides,a,modern,applicant,tracking,system,that,is,a,simple,collaborative,hiring,platform